These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, fantasy, mystery
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, orchid, daisy, sunflower
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, lilac, light-blue, turquise
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, tram, trike
1. the person who likes lilac is the person who growssunflower##1
2. the person who likes light-blue is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
3. the person who likes lilac is the person driving the bus##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
5. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
6. the person driving the tram is the person watching fantasy movies##1
7. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
8. the person who likes blue is on the far right##1
9. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | mystery   | adventure  | fantasy  |
| Flower   | orchid    | sunflower    | begonia      | daisy    |
| Color   | turquise | lilac | light-blue | blue |
| Transport     | trike  | bus       | jet-ski    | tram     |

