.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, singing, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, adventure, scientific, western
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, siglo, oliveros, swisher
There 4 different types of food: pear, lime, carrot, spinach
1. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
3. the swisher-smoker is the person eating lime##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the person watching western movies is between the oliveros-smoker and the person eating pear##2
6. the person eating spinach is between the person watching western movies and the swisher-smoker##2
7. the chaman-smoker is on the far right##1
8. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
9. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | woodworking | drawing    | singing  | cooking    |
| Movie-Genre   | action      | adventure  | western  | scientific |
| Cigar           | swisher      | oliveros       | siglo      | chaman       |
| Food         | lime    | spinach | carrot | pear |

