.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, surfing, volleyball, baseball
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, satire, horror, comedy
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, lawyer, paramedic, pilot
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, subway
1. the paramedic is the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the pilot##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
6. the lawyer is the person watching comedy movies##1
7. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
8. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching comedy movies##2
9. the person watching horror movies is between the person who's sport is volleyball and the lawyer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Sport        | surfing | volleyball     | parkour   | baseball     |
| Movie-Genre       | satire   | romance   | horror | comedy |
| Job         | analyst   | paramedic | pilot       | lawyer    |
| Transport   | roller    | motorbike | helicopter  | subway    |

