.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, mechanic, police-officer, teacher
House: futuristic, victorian, cape-cod, art-deco
4 different pets are kept: bird, frog, hamster, pony
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, british, thai, indonesian
 1. the victorian house is on the far right##1
 2. the art-deco house is the fisherman##1
 3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the indonesian##1
 4. the canadian is on the far left##1
 5. the art-deco house is the owner of the frog##1
 6. the owner of the pony is on the right of the canadian##1
 7. the victorian house is the police-officer##1
 8. the futuristic house is on the right of the art-deco house##1
 9. the fisherman is on the left of the british##1
10. the mechanic is between the owner of the bird and the teacher##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Job           | fisherman  | teacher | mechanic     | police-officer |
| House   | art-deco | futuristic  | cape-cod | victorian       |
| Pet           | frog       | pony    | hamster      | bird           |
| Nationality         | canadian | british   | indonesian   | thai         |

