.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, garlic, lemon, peach
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, mirinda, coffee
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, epic, romance, scientific
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, october, may, august
 1. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1
 3. the person drinking mirinda is the person eating garlic##1
 4. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 6. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 7. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
 8. the person drinking fanta is the person watching epic movies##1
 9. the person eating lemon is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person watching adventure movies##2
10. the person watching romance movies is the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | garlic         | lemon         | asparagus     | peach      |
| Beverage           | mirinda | coffee | cola    | fanta     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure      | romance       | scientific    | epic       |
| Birthday         | june     | may       | august | october |

