.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, freelancer, librarian, paramedic
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, baking, rock-climbing, gardening
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, polish, turkish
4 different games are played: chess, poker, monopoly, domino
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person playing domino and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
2. the freelancer is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the turkish##2
3. the polish is between the person playing poker and the dutch##2
4. the librarian is on the left of the dutch##1
5. the polish is the polish##1
6. the dutch is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
7. the dutch is on the left of the analyst##1
8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far right##1
9. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | librarian | freelancer | analyst  | paramedic |
| Hobby   | baking      | gardening       | drawing     | rock-climbing      |
| Nationality   | turkish   | dutch      | polish   | chinese   |
| Game         | monopoly   | domino    | chess | poker   |

