.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, lemonade, water
There 4 different types of food: onion, cauliflower, pineapple, raspberry
4 different pets are kept: cat, frog, horse, snake
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, ivory, turquise, blue
1. the person eating cauliflower is between the person who likes turquise and the person who likes emerald##2
2. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person drinking water##1
3. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
4. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
5. the person who likes ivory is between the person who likes turquise and the person eating onion##2
6. the person drinking lemonade is the person eating raspberry##1
7. the person drinking water is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |      3      |   4    |
| Beverage      | lemonade  | water   | iced-tea    | juice  |
| Food   | raspberry    | cauliflower   | onion | pineapple |
| Pet           | cat       | horse   | frog        | snake  |
| Color     | turquise | ivory | emerald         | blue |

