The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, designer, fisherman, social-worker
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, house, indie, metal
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, bus, car, subway
 1. the person drinking coffee is the fisherman##1
 2. the person drinking lemonade is the person driving the car##1
 3. the fisherman is the person driving the bus##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 5. the fan of metal is the person drinking tea##1
 6. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
 7. the designer is on the left of the fisherman##1
 8. the fan of house is on the far right##1
 9. the accountant is between the social-worker and the person driving the quad-bike##2
10. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage          | lemonade        | hot-chocolate    | tea | coffee   |
| Job           | social-worker | accountant | designer   | fisherman |
| Music-Genre   | indie         | folk       | metal      | house     |
