The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, baseball, soccer, cricket
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, lily, aconite, marigold
4 different pets are kept: dog, horse, rat, turtle
 1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 2. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 3. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
 4. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person drinking lemonade##1
 5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 7. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 8. the owner of the turtle is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person who's sport is soccer##2
 9. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
10. the person who growsbellflower is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person who's sport is soccer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage   | lemonade    | mirinda    | sprite      | hot-chocolate |
| Sport       | water-polo        | cricket       | soccer       | baseball     |
| Flower      | aconite | bellflower | marigold | lily        |
