City: paris, new-york, miami, marseilles
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, rowing, sailing, tennis
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, subway, train, van
 1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 4. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 5. the person traveling to new-york is between the person traveling to paris and the person traveling to marseilles##2
 6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 7. the person who's sport is tennis is the person drinking juice##1
 8. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
 9. the person traveling to marseilles is the person driving the train##1
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage        | almond-milk  | juice | fanta     | coffee     |
| City         | marseilles | new-york | paris     | miami |
| Sport       | rowing  | tennis   | biathlon | sailing    |
| Transport   | train   | subway   | jet-ski  | van        |

