 4. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 7. the person eating papaya is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the cottage house##1
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is the art-deco house##1
10. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3      |    4     |
